title: Subterranean Temple of Kallis-Zakarin
story: Kallis-Zakarin is long gone, but people are still reluctant to come close to the temple. Currently it is overrun with cats.

notes.text: An iron key at the bottom of a small pool.
An enchanted tarot deck locked in a magical safe.
An iron key in a large chest.
A huge wooden double door with two keyholes to the west.
A carving depicting a scene of inauguration.
